These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, balloon-flower, dahlia
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
3. the person who growsazalea is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| Flower    | balloon-flower    | dahlia | azalea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, house, classical
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the fan of house is in an even position##4
3. the fan of classical is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the fan of house is the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | drawing | filmmaking | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | house     | r&b        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, sudoku
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, mirinda
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | photography | baking |
| Beverage   | juice | fanta     | mirinda  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, superhero
There are 3 different nationalities: american, mexican, brazilian
1. the person watching sports movies is the mexican##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the brazilian##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports  | musical  |
| Nationality         | american  | mexican | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
City: prague, nizza, london
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, dutch
1. the person traveling to london is between the person traveling to prague and the canadian##2
2. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4
3. the dutch is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| City         | prague   | london | nizza    |
| Nationality   | colombian | dutch     | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, turkish, polish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the nigerian is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the turkish##1
3. the turkish is in an odd position##4
4. the polish is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | turkish | polish | nigerian   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, martial-arts
There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, french, egyptian
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is between the egyptian and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the indonesian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | documentary | horror |
| Nationality           | french         | indonesian         | egyptian |

