.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, kale
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, architect, nurse
1. the fisherman is between the architect and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the nurse is in an odd position##4
3. the architect is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | kale | artichoke |
| Job    | architect    | fisherman | nurse     |

