.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, funk
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, ebony, blue
1. the person who likes blue is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | dubstep  | ambient  |
| Color         | blue | ebony | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, soccer, biathlon
There 3 different types of food: corn, garlic, pineapple
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person eating pineapple is in an even position##4
3. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Sport   | surfing    | biathlon      | soccer |
| Food       | garlic | pineapple | corn   |

