.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
3 different games are played: canasta, billiard, snooker
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, subway, trike
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person driving the trike is the person playing snooker##1
4. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Game         | billiard | snooker | canasta |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, green, ebony
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
4. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Color   | ebony | green | blood-red |
| Transport     | taxi     | scooter   | van        |

