.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, drama, time-travel
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, sailing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | romance | drama   |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | cycling |

