.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, davidoff, havana
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the havana-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the owner of the pony##2
2. the davidoff-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the havana-smoker is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Cigar   | davidoff | havana | blend |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

 #################################

 
