2. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | hiking | camping   | gardening |
| Pet   | horse   | rat | goat      |

