.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
City: colone, san-francisco, miami
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| City     | san-francisco  | miami   | colone |
| Sport   | lacrosse | handball | golf       |

 